---
title: Cal Smart Turkey Corn Chowder with Garlic-Chive Ciabatta Points
description: This turkey and corn chowder is flavoured with Old Bay seasoning to kick up the flavour and bring some heat! Fully-loaded with veggies and a ciabatta dipper to boot, you'll want to make this chowder year- round!
